How to deploy a war file to heroku:
----------------------------------

1- Install the Heroku war plugin:
   $ heroku plugins:install https://github.com/heroku/heroku-deploy

2- Create your app folder

3- inside your app folder:
   $ git init

4- copy your war file into your app folder, then:
   $ git add .
   $ git commit -m "some message"

5- Now deploying to heroku:
   $ heroku deploy:war --war warFileName.war --app myappName
